          "type": "note",
          "content": "<b>Subject-Verb Agreement:</b><br>• <b>Both...and</b> = Plural verb (Both Ram <b>and</b> Shyam <b>are</b> here.)<br>• <b>Either...or / Neither...nor</b> = Verb agrees with <b>nearest subject</b> (Neither he <b>nor</b> I <b>am</b> wrong.)"
