      "content": [
        {
          "type": "list",
          "content": [
            "<b>Coordinating (FANBOYS):</b> For, And, Nor, But, Or, Yet, So - સમાન ભાગો જોડે.",
            "<b>Subordinating:</b> Because, If, When, While, Although, Unless - Main + Subordinate clause.",
            "<b>Correlative:</b> Both...and, Either...or, Neither...nor, Not only...but also - જોડીમાં.",
            "<b>Conjunctive Adverbs:</b> However, Therefore, Moreover - Semicolon સાથે.",
            "<b>Confusing:</b> When (point) vs While (duration), Until (time) vs Unless (condition).",
            "<b>Mistakes:</b> Although + but ❌, Unless + not ❌, No sooner...when ❌."
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
